---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Critical MAS blog">
	<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-800">About Critical MAS</h1>

		<div class="prose max-w-none">
			<p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
				Critical MAS is a personal blog by MAS (Michael Allen Smith), covering topics including
				economics, coffee, travel, fitness, and various other interests.
			</p>

			<h2>About the Archive</h2>
			<p>
				This site is an archived version of the blog, spanning from 2005 to 2025. The blog is no
				longer actively maintained, but all posts and comments have been preserved for posterity.
			</p>

			<h2>Topics Covered</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Economics:</strong> Personal finance, savings, and economic commentary</li>
				<li><strong>Coffee:</strong> Coffee roasting, brewing, cafe reviews</li>
				<li><strong>Travel:</strong> Trip reports and travel observations</li>
				<li><strong>Health & Fitness:</strong> Diet, exercise, and wellness</li>
				<li><strong>Technology:</strong> Various tech topics and observations</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>About MAS</h2>
			<p>
				Michael Allen Smith (MAS) is a writer and coffee enthusiast who maintained this blog for 20
				years, documenting thoughts, experiences, and insights across a wide range of topics.
			</p>

			<h2>Contact</h2>
			<p>
				This is an archived blog and comments are closed. For inquiries, you may visit the original
				site at <a href="https://criticalmas.org">criticalmas.org</a>.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
